1963;;A New Kind of Love;;American;;Melville Shavelson;;Paul Newman, Joanne Woodward, Eva Gabor;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_New_Kind_of_Love;;A womanizing American reporter assigned in Paris (Paul Newman) mistakes a cynical fashion copycat designer (Joanne Woodward) for a prostitute after she receives a makeover. He decides to interview her for a series of articles, then falls in love with her. The girl goes along with it, first out of revenge as he snubbed her during a past encounter, then out of feelings of her own.